dom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28484,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/29\/itikaf-ramadan-last-ten\/","url_meta":{"origin":19470,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: The Prophet secludes himself in the last ten nights","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 29, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would retreat to the mosque in the last ten nights of Ramadan. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2025, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1171 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":977,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/08\/05\/prophet-most-generous-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":19470,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: The Prophet was most generous in Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, was the most generous of people and he was even more generous in Ramadan when Gabriel would meet him. He would meet him every night of Ramadan to study the Quran. Thus, the Prophet would be more\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4385,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/07\/hadith-on-itikaf-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":19470,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on I&#8217;tikaf: The Prophet&#8217;s spiritual retreat in Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 7, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would seek spiritual retreat in the mosque\u00a0during the last ten nights of Ramadan, until Allah Almighty caused him to pass away. His wives continued to perform the retreat after him. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2026, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1172 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27515,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/11\/ramadan-jibreel-quran-twice\/","url_meta":{"origin":19470,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Gabriel comes to review the Quran twice","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Fatimah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGabriel would come to me to revise the Quran once every year. This year he revised with me twice. I do not think it means anything but that my term will come to an end. Verily, you will be\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0